title: New Creator: DrazeForce (Music)
body:
New member: DrazeForce
Social handle: https://www.twitch.tv/drazeforce
Community Treasury grant tier: $250
Info: DrazeForce is an Electronic Music Producer that streams his production efforts live on Twitch. 

Draze is super stoked about partnering with Rally to have empower him with more cutting edge tools to engage with his community.

He's also looking forward to coming up with innovative idea to apply creator coins in the MUSIC space. 

DrazeForce, it's a yes from me dawg - PhelpsGG
